			<p class="comment-permalink"><a href="http://terrytao.wordpress.com/2007/04/13/compressed-sensing-and-single-pixel-cameras/#comment-453" title="Permalink to this comment">14 April, 2007 at 2:08 am</a></p>
			<p class="comment-author"><strong class="fn"><a href='http://rgrig.blogspot.com/' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Radu Grigore</a></strong></p>
			 
