		<div class="comment-metadata">
			<p class="comment-permalink"><a href="http://terrytao.wordpress.com/2007/04/13/compressed-sensing-and-single-pixel-cameras/#comment-462" title="Permalink to this comment">14 April, 2007 at 3:58 pm</a></p>
			<p class="comment-author"><strong class="fn"><a href='http://botd.wordpress.com/2007/04/15/top-posts-354/' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Top Posts &laquo; WordPress.com</a></strong></p>
			 
