		<div class="comment-content">
						<p>[...] Compressed sensing and single-pixel cameras I&#8217;ve had a number of people ask me (especially in light of some recent publicity) exactly what &#8220;compressed [&#8230;] [...]</p>

<div class="pd-rating" id="pd_rating_holder_132742_comm_462"></div><script type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"><!--//--><![CDATA[//><!--
