			<p class="comment-author"><strong class="fn"><a href='http://ophir.wordpress.com/2008/01/18/smartest-person-blogging/' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Smartest Person Blogging ? &laquo; Evil Fish</a></strong></p>
			 
